{"tid":2188742,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 元朗國B仔雞翼","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T04:12:44.000Z","uid":260581,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca32a003f20ae90a6ef1311ab0ccb9c2ad0efb7","tid":2188742,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早排為左整果個譚仔 買左樽雞粉<br />\n其實我冇用雞粉煮野好幾年<br />\n為左唔好曬野 同埋我有d蒜放到爛爛地<br />\n整呢個就絕對適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一個步驟好重要<br />\n買返黎先放地下解凍 唔係你點煮都冇果個風味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWWkaSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWWkaSx.jpg&h=e3dd8388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就搵淡鹽水浸佢半個鐘同洗乾淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAXXxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAXXxR.jpg&h=a391fc53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住飛水 整走入面d污糟野<br />\n凍水落 水滾之後就可以拎出嚟 過冷河<br />\n浸冰水個皮會靚d 不過我懶 就咁沖沖水算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwvpCx7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwvpCx7.jpg&h=fcfd8cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整呢個餸 最緊要重蒜重辣<br />\n唔係食黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢到係為左清蒜 真係用多左<br />\n如果嫌麻煩既朋友仔 可以用攪拌機<br />\n如果好似我咁懶 就可以用刀切到往生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己其實覺得切出黎既蒜 有口感過攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實調味亦好少 都係紹酒 雞粉 鹽同糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6p9OFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6p9OFK.jpg&h=17f5d76d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEuqm0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEuqm0L.jpg&h=8de16c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我落左大概十湯羹紹酒<br />\n煲滾就落雞翼 加水啱啱蓋過個面<br />\n就可以落曬辣椒 一半蒜 兩匙雞粉 一匙糖 同少少鹽<br />\n先大火煲滾 然後轉細火30分鐘<br />\n呢個時候就可以落埋d蒜 然後焗佢30分鐘<br />\n記住調味唔好落得太重手 因為個汁會愈煮愈濃<br />\n唔係去到最後就咸到hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKzYG1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKzYG1F.jpg&h=9ee9946c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後開大火 收返杰個汁就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h668j6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh668j6q.jpg&h=df0f9267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n始終放過落地下 風味分加左50<br />\n不過如果想更正 可以放下路邊洗完先拎返屋企煮<br />\n食落喉嚨好C服 好惹味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMGcMMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMGcMMJ.jpg&h=676de169&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fs956MK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffs956MK.jpg&h=c8e54352&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d80b2bbc3b6ffaa8afc1e77e945d0746658548","tid":2188742,"uid":30635,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"果然係星字派 識用淡鹽水黎解凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba415f0a16106f441cb86fcdc8049a374fa3ba9","tid":2188742,"uid":293632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":